{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/calcotada-en-casa/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"A pizcas y a mizcas"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"66432846-33b9-5b5f-8759-4de4c29c15c1","excerpt":"Esta historia empezó cuando, en uno de nuestro paseos, vimos muy cerquita de casa en una verdulería : “tenemos calçots cosecha propia”. Los habíamos probado en…","html":"<p>Esta historia empezó cuando, en uno de nuestro paseos, vimos muy cerquita de casa en una verdulería : “tenemos calçots cosecha propia”.</p>\n<p>Los habíamos probado en <a href=\"/restaurantes/\" title=\"Restaurantes\">restaurantes</a> o en asadores, y esta vez nos animamos a prepararlos nosotros. Pedimos consejo a la mujer que nos lo vendió y nos pusimos manos a la obra.</p>\n<p>Los calçots se acompañan de la salsa romesco y aunque en un futuro la haremos en A Pizcas y a Mizcas, la mujer nos recomendó una que tenía ella… y la verdad es que estaba muy buena.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.65822784810127%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cal otada apm 3 pizcas\"\n        title=\"calçotada apm (3) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/828fb/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/ff44c/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/a6688/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/828fb/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/b196cd72ea5e13b67a756d2c22620dbe/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-3-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ingredientes (para dos personas)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>10 calçots</li>\n<li>aceite de oliva virgen extra</li>\n<li>salsa romesco</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cal otada apm 5 pizcas\"\n        title=\"calçotada apm (5) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/828fb/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/ff44c/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/a6688/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/828fb/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/0e85ed0ac0f0ef31a29fde3e97df1f67/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-5-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Limpiamos los calçots: recortamos parte de los tallos verdes y las barbas. Retiramos la primera capa con tierra, los colocamos en una bandeja de horno sin que estén amontonados. Les echamos un chorrito de aceite de oliva virgen extra. Precalentamos el horno a 250º grados. Introducimos la bandeja en el horno a media altura y con el grill encendido. Nosotros los tuvimos unos 10 minutos con el grill y luego lo dejamos sólo por bajo otros 15 minutos. En total unos 25 minutos de horno, para saber cuando están hecho, comprobad con unas pinzas que están tiernos.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cal otada apm 1 pizcas\"\n        title=\"calçotada apm (1) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/828fb/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/ff44c/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/a6688/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/828fb/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/8bfd8e334886c10f98aae2002e42dd32/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-1-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>La salsa venía lista para tomar, pero la suavizamos un poco con aceite de oliva virgen extra para que estuviera menos espesa.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.35443037974683%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cal otada apm 2 pizcas\"\n        title=\"calçotada apm (2) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/828fb/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/ff44c/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/a6688/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg 315w,\n/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/828fb/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg 630w,\n/static/9b60e91c7421b2bf06d9b45751ec1baf/c08c5/cal-otada-apm-2-pizcas.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A la hora de comer, se coge un calçot por la parte más verde, se le quita la “camisa” más quemada, se unta bien de salsa y se come de un bocado.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 252px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/11fb8856597dcd421dcb412d579447d8/112e4/cal-otada-apm-4-pizcas.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 190.50632911392404%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cal otada apm 4 pizcas\"\n        title=\"calçotada apm (4) (pizcas)\"\n        src=\"/static/11fb8856597dcd421dcb412d579447d8/112e4/cal-otada-apm-4-pizcas.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/11fb8856597dcd421dcb412d579447d8/ff44c/cal-otada-apm-4-pizcas.jpg 158w,\n/static/11fb8856597dcd421dcb412d579447d8/112e4/cal-otada-apm-4-pizcas.jpg 252w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>No os olvidéis del babero!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Calçotada en casa","date":"February 15, 2012","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/salmon-a-la-mostaza/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Salmón a la mostaza"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tarta-cremosa-de-capuccino/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tarta cremosa de capuccino"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"66432846-33b9-5b5f-8759-4de4c29c15c1","previousPostId":"df95bf32-9acf-53ff-af2f-cbb6106eebbe","nextPostId":"88352ba6-451e-5e4f-8083-79e40f22e129"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}